MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-402. Hendricks v. Front Row Theater. Cuyahoga County, No. 66710.

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and the same is hereby, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
